text: Md. Abdur Razzak Akand is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Joypurhat-2. ==Career== Akand was elected to parliament from Joypurhat-2 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Date of death unknown
title: Md. Abdur Razzak Akand
